# Planning dumps from parallel session windows. Large markdown briefs +
# audit reports that get scattered into the working tree by other dev
# sessions and shouldn't end up in the repo.
# NOTE: Showcase PNGs under public/showcase/ ARE intentionally committed —
# they're served via next/image at the marketing page. Do NOT blanket-
# ignore them. If you need to exclude a WIP capture, add it by full path.
